JORARepository

public JORARepository(ConnectionProvider provider,
                      String dbident)
Creates and initializes a JORA repository which will access the database identified by the supplied database identifier.

Parameters:
provider - the connection provider which will be used to obtain our database connection.
dbident - the identifier of the database that will be accessed by this repository.
